  "remarks": "Aleksandr Moroz is the General Director of the Belarusian Optical-Mechanical Association “BelOMO”. He was appointed by President Lukashenko. BelOMO is a state-owned enterprise that operates in the defence sector in Belarus, producing and selling optical sights for small arms, including telescopic sights and optical sights with illuminated reticles.",
